title: 293: 2018 NFL Draft Recap
itunes:title: 293: 2018 NFL Draft Recap
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back from the draft and ready to dive into the biggest storylines. The guys go pick by pick through the first round (2:11) before they give you their favorite selections in the draft, followed by a few head-scratching picks (29:20).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
